headline: Eli Lilly And These AI Plays Lead 5 Stocks Near Buy Points
summary: Eli Lilly, the weight-loss drug heavyweight, joins AI stocks CrowdStrike Holdings and Semtech on this weekend's watchlist of five stocks near buy points.  CrowdStrike is a leader in the emerging area of AI-driven security, while Semtech's data-center chips facilitate high performance with low power consumption.  Lilly has a 99 IBD Composite Rating out of a possible 99, according to IBD Stock Checkup.
